[h3 id=DespawnerPuffles 
	"Despawner Puffles
	$LF
]h3
[pre 
	"TODO: Add a bunch o' details n' stuff.
	$LF
]pre
[div class=p 
	"A way to do memory corruption.
	$LF
	"An Elite Puffle can drastically change an event, thus they're able to overwrite certain address set in an event script and so, despawning NPCs and change how set event works completely, until you restart the mission or said event ends with a new one.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"It's still unknown the uses it can have, but it's confirmed that it indeed corrupts memory in the games.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=PuffBuffering 
	"Puff Buffering
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Pausing the game and clicking an intended target with an Elite Puffle on the same exact frame, the puffle will hit the target while the game is paused, 
	[a class=extlink href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GfnSXOmgRrs rel=nofollow 
		"and some strange side effects might happen.
	]a
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=MovingtheMap 
	"Moving the Map
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"You can move the map with the D-pad. Unlike ingame, moving the map with the D-pad is as fast as using the stylus, so it could potentially save few frames.
	$LF
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]div
