[h3 id=PartialBlueScreenScrolling(PBSS) 
	"Partial Blue Screen Scrolling (PBSS)
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Theres 1 frame on the blue screens where you can do a touch screen input. With it you're able to do a small camera boost though is not as big as regular BSS in the sequel.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=ActivePuffleSpawning 
	"Active Puffle Spawning
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"When loading a puffle with the whistle and you currently have one already active, you can still make the puffle do the action while the other puffle is spawning.
	$LF
]div
