[h2 id=Tricks&Glitches-Herbert'sRevengeonly 
	"Tricks & Glitches - Herbert's Revenge only
	$LF
]h2
[h3 id=DoubleMenuorTripleMenu 
	"Double Menu or Triple Menu
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"This involves the Puffle selection menu and one of the other 2 menus. Get the Puffle menu open, then close it and in perfect timing, click on other menu (gadget one recommended) and the puffle menu again when its not fully closed, and you got 2 fully functional menus open! You can perform the HUD Off glitch on the Items menu to get the 3 menus open and functional at the same time!
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=PhoneCallSkip 
	"Phone Call Skip
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"During a fade in transition when you get a call, you can click on the use phone button to skip the phone call and the objective/event will be triggered instantly. This only happens on fade in transitions, not anywhere else.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=SkipMinigames 
	"Skip Minigames
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"You can only skip minigames in the sequel, not big math, just press the skip button on the screen as fast as possible and you'll skip it.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=QuickExits 
	"Quick Exits
	[img class=embedright src=https://dl.dropbox.com/s/5rj2p6ftxls84z7/Club%20Penguin%20-%20EPF%20-%20Herbert%27s%20Revenge%20%28USA%29_05_937.png 
	]img
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"After a cutscene, a minigame skip of any other specific fade to black, while clicking on an exit, the switching from room to room will glitch and it will load the next area much faster than usual.
	$LF
]div
