[h3 id=BlueScreenScrolling: 
	"Blue Screen Scrolling:
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"On the first frame when you can move the cursor on a blue screen transition, touch on the farthest pixel left/right and then move the cursor with the D-pad. If done correctly, you'll boost the camera like the Puffle Scrolling Glitch.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=CoinGlitch 
	"Coin Glitch
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"The earliest known glitch 
	[a class=extlink href=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8e6SS7mMaaE rel=nofollow 
		"found back in 2010.
	]a
	" After beating a minigame with a set amount of coins, you can choose a level/minigame, then Start+Quit the level, you'll get the coins you got in the previous level you've done. Extremely useful in 100% runs to skip long levels and get gold medals much earlier.
	$LF
]div
